fields.short_description: 3 bedroom 2 storey semi-detached house, U Citywest Demesne, Citywest, Co. Dublin
fields.description: U Citywest Demesne is a fabulous development of luxury new homes, located beside numerous amenities & schools. The redbrick Edwardian style houses take their inspiration from Dublin's redbrick streetscapes, and the Demesne has a beautiful landscaped 'village green' at the heart of the estate. The 3 & 4 bedroom homes are all generously proportioned and are fully finished with high quality kitchens (including appliances) and bathrooms. The quality finish is complimented by bespoke U furniture and finishes throughout.

fields.short_description: 3-Bed Townhouses, Opus, 6 Hanover Quay, Hanover Quay, Dublin 2
fields.description: Savills is delighted to present Opus at 6 Hanover Quay in the centre of Dublin's Docklands to the rental market. Set apart from all other residential offerings in the city at present, Opus at 6 Hanover Quay offers residents a unique living experience in this striking building featuring 120 individual homes. Living at Opus will offer residents a range of exclusive amenities and a level of service that is second to none.

fields.short_description: Twin Bed Sharing, Archway Court, 39A Mountjoy Street, Dublin 7
fields.description: Twin Single Sharing Room for rent at Archway Court Shared Student Accommodation complex. Each room contains two single beds.  The house has an open-plan shared sitting and dining area, with a fully fitted kitchen, spacious bedrooms, and a number of bathrooms.
